| {{flag|Yemen}} {{anchor|Y}}
| Life + 30 years
| • 10 years from the date of issue from January 1 of the year of issue for photographs;<br>
• 25 years from the date of production from January 1 of the production year for motion picture or television film.<ref name="Yemen">{{cite web |title=Intellectual Property Law. Law No. 19 for the Year 1994. |format=PDF |work=Official Gazette No. 20 issued on 27 Jumada I, 1415 A.H. corresponding to 31 October 1994 |date=1994-10-31 |url=http://www.wipo.int/edocs/lexdocs/laws/en/ye/ye004en.pdf |accessdate=2014-04-13}}</ref>

After expiry of copyright, the work "''may'' be announced to be the ownership of the State" (emphasis added).<ref name="Yemen" />
